name: VOXELFINE #6: "The Thinker" by Auguste Rodin 3D voxelart model (.glb)
description: The first non-painting Voxelfine! It's also the first piece in grayscale, which I found a little harder to work in. Voxelfines are collectible 3D voxel models of iconic works of art. They are ready to be imported into a VR or AR experience of your choice. By Lorem Ipsum, 2021.
